      "type": "Section"
    },
    "Notes": {
      "children": [
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "The similar function in MATLAB is called "
            },
            {
              "domain": null,
              "role": null,
              "type": "Directive",
              "value": "grpdelay"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "If the transfer function "
            },
            {
              "type": "inlineMath",
              "value": "H(z)"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": " has zeros or poles on the unit circle, the group delay at corresponding frequencies is undefined. When such a case arises the warning is raised and the group delay is set to 0 at those frequencies."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "For the details of numerical computation of the group delay refer to ."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
